    "about_story": {
      "type": "postcard-about-story",
      "blocks": {
        "p1": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Hi, I’m Hildra.<br/><br/>I didn’t start POSTCARD to build a beauty brand—I started it because of my eczema.<br/><br/>For a long time, I relied on steroid creams just to keep things under control. Personal care didn’t feel like something I could enjoy—it felt clinical, something I had to manage carefully.<br/><br/>At some point, I knew I wanted to step away from that cycle.<br/>I wanted something simpler. Gentler. Safer.<br/><br/>So I began making my own.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "p2": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Formulations that focus only on what the skin truly needs—nothing excessive, nothing harsh. But just as importantly, I wanted to bring back the experience. To turn something routine into something you could actually enjoy.<br/><br/>That’s where Postcard moments come in—small, sensorial pauses in your day. An everyday touch of luxury that everyone deserves to enjoy, designed to transport you through the world of scent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p3": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>And as we create, we think beyond just the product. Through refills and reusable bottles, we’re always working to reduce single-use waste—because care should extend to the world around us too.<br/><br/>Everything we create is considered—from the ingredients we choose to the way it feels in your hands—because we want to leave the world a little more postcard perfect than we found it.<br/><br/>—Hildra</p>"
          }
        }
      },
